div.div: Dororo, a young orphan thief, meets Hyakkimaru, a powerful ronin. Hyakkimaru's father, a greedy feudal lord, had made a pact with 12 demons, offering his yet-unborn son's body parts in exchange for great power. Thus, Hyakkimaru - who was born without arms, legs, eyes, ears, a nose or a mouth - was abandoned in a river as a baby. Rescued and raised by Dr. Honma, who equips him with artificial limbs and teaches him sword-fighting techniques, Hyakkimaru discovers that each time he slays a demon, a piece of his body is restored. Now, he roams the war-torn countryside in search of demons.

Unable to hear, speak, or wield a sword, Prince Bojji doesn’t seem like a typical heir to the throne—and his kingdom agrees. But his fateful encounter with Kage, a shadow on the ground, gives him his first true friend. The two set off on a grand adventure and, together, form a bond that can overcome any obstacle...even being king.
(Source: Funimation)
Watashi Yori Tsuyoi Otoko to Kekkon Shitai no Seiso Bijin Seito Kaichou (Jitsuha Moto Banchou) no Himitsu wo shiru Kage Kya (Jitsuha Kanojo wo Koeru Saikyou no Yankee)

Akira Kogure, a boy who was a bit of a nerd, accidentally discovered that the beautiful student council president, Shizuka Takasaki, used to be a delinquent girl-gang leader. She said she would only marry a man who was stronger than her. But it turned out that Akira was actually also a former delinquent even stronger than her.
(Source: Fantasia Bunko, translated)
Hahaoya ga Ero Ranobe Taishou Jushou Shite Jinsei Tsunda: Semete Musuko no Love Come ni Mazaranai de Kudasai

Life Is A Mess Since My Mom Won An Ero-Novel Grand Prize~ At Least Don’t Mess With Your Son’s Romantic Comedy!
My life is in hard mode because of my mother who loves me so much!
A mother-son incest Ero-Novel written by a mother, Mirei, was somehow able to win the grand prize, but for some reason, her son was the one who attended and received the reward? That’s ridiculous! Ahem! nevermind I mean it’s cliche. Furthermore, a current JK author who also won the award at the same time is also… yesh the MC’s crush.
To explain it further It’s a story about the MC’s life with a son-con mother who’s also an upcoming author for a sensual novel.
